{"tid":2451763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場踢爆： 高志森向大公報投訴只獲藝發局資助幾萬  實際其實已獲批資助30萬！！","createTime":"2021-03-18T10:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T12:36:52.000Z","uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b05b666ac32d68796666b0f68609c37dd781784","tid":2451763,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T10:23:59.000Z","msg":"親中導演高志森於《大公報》訪問中聲稱，藝發局僅撥出數萬港元予由其監製的舞台劇《金鎖記》作昆明站演出。惟《立場》翻查藝發局文件發現該項目獲批 30 多萬港元。就疑「報細數」一事，《立場》今早曾向高志森查詢，未獲回覆。直到下午三時左右，高志森才自行發影片澄清，指受訪時身邊同事給予「唔完整資訊」，《金鎖記》獲批資助應為 30 萬，非幾萬元，就資料有誤「同《大公報》講聲唔好意思」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3991504984268425/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3991504984268425%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2YaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=f18daf69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3991504984268425/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"d129b4e8ffc33f007a0b06097008a608432a6295","tid":2451763,"uid":188176,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T10:25:57.000Z","msg":"佢大話慣犯黎"},{"pid":"4e8e9077bde97ca916b02864b3c9b84016fed1af","tid":2451763,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T10:26:31.000Z","msg":"佢睇錯貨幣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cba92854f654d344bc42c279fc16a05fb5db57","tid":2451763,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T10:40:36.000Z","msg":"又fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2790045d8ff4922b48b56b80af2754ec6c180168","tid":2451763,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy